OL,3,CJailed driver was 'speeding and using
OL,4,Cphone' before fatal crash
OL,6,FA woman who was using her phone before
OL,7,Fa crash which killed a woman and
OL,8,Finjured a man, has been jailed.
OL,10,FRomeesa Ahmed, 27, was speeding in her
OL,11,FVolkswagen Golf before it collided
OL,12,Fwith a bus stop on Stanningley Road on
OL,13,F22 February 2023.
OL,15,FMature student, Athira Anilkumar Laly
OL,16,FKumari, died at the scene.
