OL,3,CJailed driver was 'speeding and using
OL,4,Cphone' before fatal crash
OL,6,FWest Yorkshire Police said the 28-year-
OL,7,Fold came to England, leaving her young
OL,8,Fdaughter behind, to "better herself"
OL,9,Fand create a future for her and her
OL,10,Ffamily.
OL,12,FAn investigation found Ahmed had been
OL,13,Fspeeding and using her mobile phone at
OL,14,Fthe time of the crash.
OL,16,FAthira's family said their much-loved
OL,17,Fdaughter was the foundation of their
OL,18,Ffamily.
