OL,6,F"She was not just a member of our
OL,7,Ffamily ` she was our foundation, the
OL,8,Fglue that held us all together. A
OL,9,Floving daughter, a devoted wife, a
OL,10,Fdoting mother and a source of light
OL,11,Fand inspiration to everyone who knew
OL,12,Fher.
OL,14,F"Athira was the heart of our lives.
OL,15,FHer absence has left a void so deep,
OL,16,Fso profound, that even words fail to
OL,17,Fconvey the magnitude of our grief."
