OL,6,FA 40-year-old man, who was waiting at
OL,7,Fthe bus stop, suffered serious
OL,8,Finjuries and had an extensive stay in
OL,9,Fhospital.
OL,11,FRomeesa Ahmed, of Princeville Street
OL,12,Fin Bradford, was handed a nine year
OL,13,Fsentence for causing death by
OL,14,Fdangerous driving and causing serious
OL,15,Finjury by dangerous driving.
OL,17,FShe was also given an 11-year driving
OL,18,Fban and will need to pass a further
OL,19,Ftest before she can obtain a driving
OL,20,Flicence again.
