OL,6,FSpeaking after the sentence, Detective
OL,7,FConstable Adele Murphy-Hartley, said
OL,8,Fit should be a warning to everyone
OL,9,Fabout the consequences of using a
OL,10,Fphone while driving.
OL,12,FShe said: "This should be a warning to
OL,13,Fall of what can happen when these
OL,14,Ffactors come into play.
