OL,6,F"Athira made the difficult decision to
OL,7,Fleave her young daughter in the care
OL,8,Fof family, and now her young daughter
OL,9,Fwill have to grow up not knowing her
OL,10,Fmother. Her husband has been widowed
OL,11,Fand her parents have been left to deal
OL,12,Fwith the death of their much-loved
OL,13,Fdaughter.
OL,15,F"Ahmed's actions have also resulted in
OL,16,Fthe life of one man being changed
OL,17,Fforever, both physically and mentally."
